Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.02,0:02:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Countless pirates fight\Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the great treasure left behind\Nby Gold Roger, the Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.79,0:03:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body\Nturned to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.63,0:03:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,also takes to the sea\Nto become the next Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,As Luffy and his friends\Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the World Government is less and less\Nable to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.45,0:03:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.91,0:03:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What adventure is waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.18,0:03:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.63,0:03:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Separated from the rest of the Straw Hats,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.80,0:03:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy is rushing to Navy HQ to rescue his brother, Ace,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.97,0:03:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,who is waiting to be executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.17,0:03:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The execution is in 3 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.97,0:03:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All forces of the Navy are expecting an attack by the Whitebeard Pirates at Marineford.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.95,0:03:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace, tell them the name of your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:03:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My father is Whitebeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.19,0:04:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.33,0:04:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother's name is Portgas D. Rouge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.90,0:04:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A year and 3 months after the father's death,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the child was born with the blood\Nof the world's most heinous man in his veins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.31,0:04:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Pirate King—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Still?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.07,0:04:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The bloodline of the Pirate King?!
