Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that the arch villain had a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The legend of Gold Roger continues!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so relieved that they got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's a son of the Pirate King,\Nhe must be atrocious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.87,0:05:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'd caught him and put him up for auction,\NI would have made a fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.41,0:05:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This execution is turning into quite a show!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So Fire Fist got his strength from his father?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, does he have the One Piece, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire Fist is as good as dead anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He will be wiped off the face of the earth soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:04.01,"Sign",,0,0,0,,{\fad(920,100)}"Navy"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He is not the biological brother of Luffy, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.47,0:06:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...Son?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,His biological son alive! This must be a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.12,0:06:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All people connected to Roger\Nshould have been executed at that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.69,0:06:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Since his brother is Luffy-san,\NI thought that his father was Dragon, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought so, too! What's the deal here?\NThey're not biological brothers?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.77,0:07:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Garp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.91,0:07:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Garp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you believe this, Garp?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.05,0:07:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm expecting a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.72,0:07:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I won't be around by the time of the child's birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:08:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why're you telling that to me a Navy officer, Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The mother of the child—a woman related to you will be executed for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.95,0:08:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The Government will definitely dig up\Nmy whereabouts for the last year
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and find and kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.79,0:08:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But they can't blame a child whose not born.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We've tried to kill each other dozens of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I can trust you as I trust my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.25,0:08:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You must protect my baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.59,0:09:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop being so selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.70,0:09:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm sure that you'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.87,0:09:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Look after my child!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:10:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure that it's this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,People saw Roger acting like he wasn't a pirate here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.52,0:10:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,As if he were a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger's era has ended.\NWe have to cut the bloodline.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Find all the babies who are due within 10 months of his going to jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All pregnant women, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.55,0:10:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill all mothers who are suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,5 were born in this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.01,0:11:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ones who are due next month are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.52,0:11:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Look into the ones with husbands, too.\NThey could be fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll come back when she is cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.65,0:12:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't come out yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.67,0:12:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.44,0:12:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.68,0:12:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet. Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.69,0:12:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.99,0:12:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There're no more pregnant women.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.03,0:13:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been 10 months since Roger went to jail.\NI don't think he has a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So Roger's time is really over, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.16,0:13:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Portgas D. Rouge, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's a girl—Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's a boy—Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.21,0:13:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are the names that he picked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.82,0:13:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So his name is Gol D. Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Our son.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Rouge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.42,0:14:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Rouge! Stay with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.90,0:14:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You must raise him, Dadan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.50,0:14:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.14,0:14:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose baby is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Dadan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.63,0:15:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. You're gonna live with them from today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.03,0:15:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta live with them! Be nice to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.81,0:15:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Luffy and I unfortunately have the blood of...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.55,0:15:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...the world's most infamous criminals in our veins anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I took over the name "Portgas"\Nfrom my mother to whom I owe so much
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.69,0:15:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but I never wanted to have\Nmy good-for-nothing father's blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.53,0:15:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My only father is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.33,0:15:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.61,0:15:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Garp.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It was 2 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.95,0:16:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You took over your mother's name and rose up in the world of the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.88,0:16:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...as the captain of the Spade Pirates with your exquisite speed and power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.39,0:16:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's when we noticed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.59,0:16:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...that Roger's blood still flowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But Whitebeard also noticed that at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And to make you the next Pirate King,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,he let the son of his old rival onto his ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.45,0:16:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I got on the ship to make my dad the next King!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No one believes that except you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.96,0:16:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, it made it harder for us to catch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You were protected by Whitebeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.27,0:17:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If we let you go free, we know you'll use your abilities to become the next King.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.44,0:17:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it means a great deal\Nto execute you here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.58,0:17:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it means risking\Nan all-out war with Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.03,0:17:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Fleet Admiral Sengoku! I have report!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.76,0:17:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gates of Justice are opening without any order.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.87,0:17:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And we can't make contact with the control room!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.27,0:17:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be nice if they opened with a hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.32,0:17:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, like "knock knock"...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You think that's all it'd take?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They're opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.07,0:18:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.84,0:18:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gates of Justice are opening on their own!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The Navy guy told us that they weren't gonna open the gates!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The control room must be\Nin Marineford. Who is doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.69,0:18:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go! A little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.13,0:18:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it because...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.83,0:18:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...out of joy, my blade bones are dancing the lambada!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There! There! There we go, there we go, there we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ca-Captain Buggy, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.34,0:18:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.75,0:18:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that you're opening them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.78,0:18:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a messenger of God?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.28,0:18:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true, Buggy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not! What kind of role play is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.39,0:19:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But seriously. Who is opening them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.36,0:19:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe God really wants me to become the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.51,0:19:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares! In any case...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.27,0:19:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.73,0:19:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's almost unnatural.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.46,0:20:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.29,0:20:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, battle stations!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They appeared so suddenly! Where did they get in?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a vast fleet of pirate ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.45,0:20:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Whitebeard? Look for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.16,0:20:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"Bohemian Knight" Doma!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.93,0:20:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,"Thunder Lord" McGuy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The DeCalvan Brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"Whirl Spider" Squard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.50,0:20:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all big-time captains\Nwho are well known in the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.30,0:21:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,43 ships in total! We can't find Whitebeard or the commanders!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.18,0:21:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're all allies of Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace-chan, can you see us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.22,0:21:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here for you, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.39,0:21:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't panic! So pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.19,0:21:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect them to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.30,0:21:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.60,0:21:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Whitebeard should be somewhere near, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.23,0:21:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And he must be up to something so keep an eye on the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.67,0:21:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.84,0:21:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting excited! Just come on, Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.43,0:21:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.94,0:22:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.77,0:22:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he'll appear from where we least expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.68,0:22:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we got the wrong lineup.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.19,0:22:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I see a shadow in the bay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.12,0:22:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.94,0:22:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it now! They got all their ships...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...coated and approached from underwater!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.23,0:22:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Here comes Moby Dick!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.18,0:23:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The Moby Dick emerges\Nright in the middle of Marineford.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.32,0:23:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,On its deck, Whitebeard\Nand his 14 commanders are ready for battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.69,0:23:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The Whitebeard Pirates head straight for Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.63,0:23:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There is an unbroken bond\Nbetween them an Ace, a family bond!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.50,0:23:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.97,0:23:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Beginning of the War! Ace and Whitebeard's Past"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.14,0:23:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
